This is a small hideout i have made. There will be updates
The entrance is behind Breezehome in Whiterun
Contains:
>full crafting room
>Garden
>Semi-furnished Bedroom
>Armory with 64 Weapon racks \"1 more each basic weapon\"
and 8 Mannequins \"1 for each bacis armor type\"
>Half of a book shelf is working in the crafting room
I wil be adding more Rack\'s, Mannequins and book shelfs soon.
